Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.76,0:02:22.66,ED ロマ字,,0,0,0,,{\c&He35cd4&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Kakeagatte mitara sotto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:27.06,ED ロマ字,,0,0,0,,{\c&He35cd4&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Kaze o kīte mite kitto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:30.04,ED ロマ字,,0,0,0,,{\c&He35cd4&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Kokoro harete iku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.13,0:02:35.14,ED ロマ字,,0,0,0,,{\c&He35cd4&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Harō harō harō kocchi da yo
